{"word":"τέκμαρ","slug":"τέκμαρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n102842\" key=\"te/kmar\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τέκμαρ</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τέκμωρ</orth> (so always in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, never elsewhere), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <itype opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ indecl.\">indecl.</a></itype>:—<sense id=\"n102842.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fixed mark</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">boundary, goal, end</tr_> (= <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πέρας, κατὰ τὴν ἀρχαίαν γλῶσσαν</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg038.perseus-grc1:1357b:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1357b9</biblScope> </bibl>), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἵκετο τέκμωρ</foreign> he reached the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">goal</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.20</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοῖο μὲν . . εὕρετο τέκμωρ</foreign> for this he found <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">an end</tr_>, i.e. devised <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a remedy</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:472\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.472</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰς ὅ κε τ. Ἰλίου εὕρωσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:30\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.30</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐδέ τι τέκμωρ εὑρέμεναι δύνασαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:373\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.373</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:466\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">466</biblScope> </bibl>: in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author></bibl>, either <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">end, termination</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τέκμαρ αἰῶνος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg005:165\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">165</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">end, object, purpose, P.</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg005:2:49\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.49</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n102842.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fixed line</tr_> of separation, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δειλῶν τε καὶ ἐσθλῶν τ. ἐναργές</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg007:164\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">164</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n102842.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sure sign</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">token</tr_> of some high and solemn kind, as Zeus says that his nod is <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐξ ἐμέθεν μέγιστον τέκμωρ</foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the highest, surest pledge</tr_> I can give, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:526\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.526</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σαφὲς τ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg003.perseus-grc1:11:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">N.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.44</biblScope> </bibl>; of the moon, as <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a sign</tr_> in the heavens, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τ. δὲ βροτοῖς . . τέτυκται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg032.perseus-grc1:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ h.Hom.\">h.Hom.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">32.13</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:499\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.499</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:1002\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.1002</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦν δ᾽ οὐδὲν αὐτοῖς οὔτε χείματος τ. οὔτ᾽ . . ἦρος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg003.perseus-grc1:454\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">454</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔστι τῶνδέ σοι τ</foreign>.; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:272\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">272</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:315\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">315</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τἀνδρὸς ἐκφανὲς τ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg007.perseus-grc1:244\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eu.\">Eu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">244</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῆσδ᾽ ἀφίξεως τ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg001.perseus-grc1:483\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Supp.\">Supp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">483</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κυνὸς . . σῆμα, ναυτίλοις τ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1273\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hec.\">Hec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1273</biblScope></bibl>.--Poet. word, used also in the <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Prose of <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> </bibl> and <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aret.</author> </bibl> for <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">symptom</tr_>, esp. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pathognomic symptom</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg036:2:123\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mul.\">Mul.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.123</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0719.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aret.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SA\">SA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.2</biblScope></bibl>, al.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}